name: SupremeCourtofIndia
0:
”Alexa, open supreme court.”
”Ask Supreme Court about my cases for tomorrow.”
”Ask Supreme Court to fetch the causelist for AOR 1234 for next Monday.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: supreme court
des:
Have you ever missed out on an important court case as a lawyer due to your busy schedule? This skill is just what you need - it can tell you about your cases at the Supreme Court of India.

* Currently available only for the Supreme Court of India. Please contact the developer if you'd like to see this for other courts and in other countries too!
